    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Chief Complaint:  Altered Mental Status    HPI:    Ms [**Known lastname 3824**] ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s1",
      "text": "Chief Complaint:  Altered Mental Status    HPI:    Ms [**Known lastname 3824**] is a 55 yo F with diabetes, colon cancer, treated in    [**2141**]-[**2142**] with resection and chemotherapy, complicated by cirrhosis."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "She has had no evidence recurrence on imaging including PET scan, but    CEAs ha",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s2",
      "text": "She has had no evidence recurrence on imaging including PET scan, but    CEAs have been trending upward (thought to be due to liver    inflammation)."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Pt admitted intially on [**8-27**] for shortness of breath, AMS, confusion,    l",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s3",
      "text": "Pt admitted intially on [**8-27**] for shortness of breath, AMS, confusion,    lethargy x 48hrs thought to be hepatic encephalopathy, given elevated    ammonia, treated with Lactulose."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Also given fluids, dopamine,    Levo/Vanco for hypotension.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s4",
      "text": "Also given fluids, dopamine,    Levo/Vanco for hypotension."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "On [**8-30**], pt developed respiratory distress    and hypoxemia, was intubated",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s5",
      "text": "On [**8-30**], pt developed respiratory distress    and hypoxemia, was intubated and treated for ARDS."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Pt improved and vent    was weaned but pt's mental status did not improve with r",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s6",
      "text": "Pt improved and vent    was weaned but pt's mental status did not improve with removal of    sedation."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "She was worked up with EEG (toxic metabolic slowing), head CT    (negative), Neu",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s7",
      "text": "She was worked up with EEG (toxic metabolic slowing), head CT    (negative), Neuro consult (brain stem reflexes intact but decreased    higher cortical function."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:8",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Considered etiologies remained hepatic    encephalopathy with ongoing treatment ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s8",
      "text": "Considered etiologies remained hepatic    encephalopathy with ongoing treatment with Lactulose and Rifaximin and    good stooling response, as well as slowed clearance of sedating    medications used while intubated given obesity. trached on [**9-17**] with    Shiley trach."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:9",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Course also complicated by recurrent fevers to 101-102.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s9",
      "text": "Course also complicated by recurrent fevers to 101-102."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:10",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "All cultures    negative, including lines (central line pulled last week).",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s10",
      "text": "All cultures    negative, including lines (central line pulled last week)."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:11",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Bronchoscopy    negative except [**Female First Name (un) 444**].",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s11",
      "text": "Bronchoscopy    negative except [**Female First Name (un) 444**]."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:12",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "No evidence of ascites on US or abd scans.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s12",
      "text": "No evidence of ascites on US or abd scans."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:13",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Gallbladder was shown to be enlarged and PCBD was placed on [**9-2**].",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s13",
      "text": "Gallbladder was shown to be enlarged and PCBD was placed on [**9-2**]."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:14",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "[**Name (NI) 8805**], pt persistently had normal renal function (Cr 0.7-1) and g",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s14",
      "text": "[**Name (NI) 8805**], pt persistently had normal renal function (Cr 0.7-1) and good    urine output, until day of transfer when Cr bumped to 1.5 and pt    developed hematuria."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:15",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Other issues have been persistent thrombocytopenia (60s-120s),    coagulopathy (",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s15",
      "text": "Other issues have been persistent thrombocytopenia (60s-120s),    coagulopathy (INR 1.5-1.7, no bleeding)."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row600430:16",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Given h/o gastric lap banding,    surgery had to release band for OG placement.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row600430#s16",
      "text": "Given h/o gastric lap banding,    surgery had to release band for OG placement."
    },
    {
